name: ACTION Food Pantry
review_text: I was homeless for many years and action pantry has been 1 of the ways I was able to eat..sometimes the only way! They are some of the most sweetest, hardworking people from Mr.Rick to Mrs. Cathy..and ALL of the AWESOME PEOPLE that give their love and support and time.They have a WHOLE ENTIRE NETWORK RUNNING from here to there and so forth and wherever something is needed they have wonderful people that contribute to the cause of making sure no one is hungry..
